Bum Ghost: Greetings again, C.G. I was thinking about what we talked about the other day, and... I think you were right.
Bum Ghost: Still, I don't agree that happiness is everything in life, but it certainly doesn't help if I keep telling myself it sucked, no?
Bum Ghost: Besides, all of the ghosts here have their reasons for being here, right?
Bum Ghost: They all have problems, and they're all dissatisfied in some way. Now, I still think that my reasons are a bit more... concerning, but I suppose it's all about perspective.
<<emotionChange Ponder>>
Bum Ghost: What I'm trying to say is... thanks, Caf-Caf. ...For listening to me and for talking with me. You're a great guy, y'know that?
Bum Ghost: ...What am I gonna do now?
<<emotionChange Smug Sparkles>>
Bum Ghost: Aren't you nosy, Cafe. Kidding, kidding.
<<emotionChange Ponder>>
Bum Ghost: I think... I'll wander for a bit. Until my metaphorical legs tire. 
Bum Ghost: And when I'm ready, I want to see what the other ghosts are up to. That tycoon monocle dude is trying to make something, and he even got the column guy to help.
Bum Ghost: I think... I miss my parents. They're not gone yet, but one day they will come.
<<emotionChange Smug>>
Bum Ghost: When they do... I want to disappear with them. I don't know what comes next, but I want to confront whatever it is with them.
Bum Ghost: Thanks, Caf. I'll be seeing you.
<<emotionChange Normal>>
<<setCam "Main Camera">>
